    <briefdescription>
<para>The TrajectoryDMPLearner encapsulates the dmp learning process. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Dynamic movement primitives can be easily learned by using this class and providing the cartesian data or a file containing this data. Basically this is a helper that enables the programmer to reduce code complexity. </para>    </detaileddescription>
